Channels Connection on the DI Water washing Machine with 4 Ports: We will use the ASP Vina serial Interface For each Port we have a Switch for the Pump and a 3 way valve to switch from Water to Air. --------------------------------------------------------------- Port 1 : Relay 1 : (3 Way Valve Air/Water) Relay 8 : (Pump On/Off) Light Tower 1 : Relays 9,10,11,12 (RYGB) Relay 22 : Reverse Flow (switch 3 x 3Ways valves simultaneous)
ADV1: Analog Air Pressure ADC1: Analog Water Pressure ADA1: Analog Flow Rate --------------------------------------------------------------- Port 2 : Relay 2 : (3 Way Valve Air/Water) Relay 7 : (Pump On/Off Light Tower 2: Relays 13,14,15,16 (RYGB) Relay 23 : Reverse Flow (switch 3 x 3Ways valves simultaneous)
ADV2: Analog Air Pressure ADC2: Analog Water Pressure ADA2: Analog Flow Rate --------------------------------------------------------------- Port 3 : Relay 3 : (3 Way Valve Air/Water) Relay 6 : (Pump On/Off Light Tower 3 : Relays 17,18,19,20 (RYGB) Relay 24 : Reverse Flow (switch 2 x 3Ways valves simultaneous)
ADV3: Analog Air Pressure ADC3: Analog Water Pressure ADA3: Analog Flow Rate ---------------------------------------------------------------
